text: Luchsingen was a municipality, in the municipality of Glarus Süd and canton of Glarus in Switzerland. On 1 January 2004, the former municipalities of Hätzingen and Diesbach were merged into the municipality of Luchsingen. Oberblegisee is in the municipality. ==Other websites== * Official website Category:Former municipalities of Glarus Category:2011 disestablishments in Switzerland
